#. <section class="sutta" id="sn3.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Shackles"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Yaññasutta"
msgstr "9. Sacrifice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.76"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn3.9:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena rañño pasenadissa kosalassa mahāyañño paccupaṭṭhito "
"hoti, pañca ca usabhasatāni pañca ca vacchatarasatāni pañca ca "
"vacchatarisatāni pañca ca ajasatāni pañca ca urabbhasatāni thūṇūpanītāni "
"honti yaññatthāya."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time a big sacrifice had been set up for King Pasenadi of "
"Kosala. Five hundred chief bulls, five hundred bullocks, five hundred "
"heifers, five hundred goats, and five hundred rams had been led to the "
"pillar for the sacrifice."

msgctxt "sn3.9:1.3"
msgid ""
"Yepissa te honti dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, tepi daṇḍatajjitā "
"bhayatajjitā assumukhā rudamānā parikammāni karonti."
msgstr ""
"His bondservants, employees, and workers did their jobs under threat of "
"punishment and danger, weeping with tearful faces."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.173"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pavisiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants robed up in the morning and, taking their bowls and "
"robes, entered Sāvatthī for alms."

msgctxt "sn3.9:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. "
"Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then, after the meal, when they returned from alms-round, they went up to "
"the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what was happening."

msgctxt "sn3.9:2.3"
msgid ""
"“idha, bhante, rañño pasenadissa kosalassa mahāyañño paccupaṭṭhito hoti, "
"pañca ca usabhasatāni pañca ca vacchatarasatāni pañca ca vacchatarisatāni "
"pañca ca ajasatāni pañca ca urabbhasatāni thūṇūpanītāni honti yaññatthāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.9:2.4"
msgid ""
"Yepissa te honti dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, tepi daṇḍatajjitā "
"bhayatajjitā assumukhā rudamānā parikammāni karontī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etamatthaṃ viditvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, knowing the meaning of this, on that occasion the Buddha recited these "
"verses:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:4.1"
msgid "“Assamedhaṃ purisamedhaṃ,"
msgstr "“Horse sacrifice, human sacrifice,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:4.2"
msgid "sammāpāsaṃ vājapeyyaṃ;"
msgstr "the sacrifices of the ‘stick-casting’,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Niraggaḷaṃ mahārambhā → vājapeyyaṃ niraggaḷaṃ; mahāyaññā mahārambhā (bj, s1-3, km) | vājapeyyaṃ; niraggaḷaṃ mahārambhā (pts1) | vājapeyyaṃ niraggalaṃ mahāyaññā mahārambhā (pts2)
msgctxt "sn3.9:4.3"
msgid "Niraggaḷaṃ mahārambhā,"
msgstr "the ‘royal soma drinking’, and the ‘unbarred’—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:4.4"
msgid "na te honti mahapphalā."
msgstr "these huge violent sacrifices yield no great fruit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:5.1"
msgid "Ajeḷakā ca gāvo ca,"
msgstr "The great sages of good conduct"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:5.2"
msgid "vividhā yattha haññare;"
msgstr "don’t attend sacrifices"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:5.3"
msgid "Na taṃ sammaggatā yaññaṃ,"
msgstr "where goats, sheep, and cattle"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:5.4"
msgid "upayanti mahesino."
msgstr "and various creatures are killed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.174"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:6.1"
msgid "Ye ca yaññā nirārambhā,"
msgstr "But the great sages of good conduct"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:6.2"
msgid "yajanti anukulaṃ sadā;"
msgstr "do attend non-violent sacrifices"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:6.3"
msgid "Ajeḷakā ca gāvo ca,"
msgstr "of regular family tradition,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:6.4"
msgid "vividhā nettha haññare;"
msgstr "where goats, sheep, and cattle,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:6.5"
msgid "Etaṃ sammaggatā yaññaṃ,"
msgstr "and various creatures aren’t killed."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:6.6"
msgid "upayanti mahesino."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.9:7.1"
msgid "Etaṃ yajetha medhāvī,"
msgstr "A clever person should sacrifice like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:7.2"
msgid "eso yañño mahapphalo;"
msgstr "for this sacrifice is very fruitful."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:7.3"
msgid "Etañhi yajamānassa,"
msgstr "For a sponsor of sacrifices like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:7.4"
msgid "seyyo hoti na pāpiyo;"
msgstr "things get better, not worse."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:7.5"
msgid "Yañño ca vipulo hoti,"
msgstr "Such a sacrifice is truly abundant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.9:7.6"
msgid "pasīdanti ca devatā”ti."
msgstr "and even the deities are pleased.”"
